Package: fancyr
Type: Package
Title: Fancy Statistics for Correlational (r) Analyses 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dustin Wood
Maintainer: Dustin Wood <dustin.wood@cba.ua.edu>
Description: Provides functions for correlational and measurement analyses,
    including reliability-adjusted correlation matrices, scale-centered correlations
    (Cohen, 1969), clusters of validity-relevant items, dimensionality assessment,
    data screening utilities (e.g., proportion of maximum possible standard deviation),
    and data transformations (e.g., POMP scores and scale-center-deviation scores).
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/Dustin-Wood/fancyr
BugReports: https://github.com/Dustin-Wood/fancyr/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
